entries.journal_entry_description: Visit Gendra, who knows about crafting and entertaining.
entries.task00_comm_message_text: When you have a free moment, come by and see me. I have much to discuss with you, and perhaps some work that you can do for me.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Gendra sent you a message and asked you to come speak with him. You should find him and see what he wants.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Now that you've found Gendra you should speak with him.
